---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PillarCard from '../components/PillarCard.astro';
import AvatarCard from '../components/AvatarCard.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Crown and Compass | A Brotherhood for Men"
  description="A peer-led Christian men's community built around reading, honest conversation, and The Walk. Free. No ranks. No performance."
>

  <!-- ============================ HERO ============================ -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <svg class="hero-rose" viewBox="0 0 200 200" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
      <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="96" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" />
      <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="70" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.6" />
      <polygon points="100,10 108,92 100,100 92,92" fill="currentColor" />
      <polygon points="100,190 92,108 100,100 108,108" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.55" />
      <polygon points="190,100 108,92 100,100 108,108" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.55" />
      <polygon points="10,100 92,108 100,100 92,92" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.55" />
    </svg>
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <p class="kicker">A brotherhood for men</p>
        <h1 class="hero-headline">The Walk is long.<br />No man takes it alone.</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtext">
          A small group of Christian men who read a book together and talk honestly
          about their lives. Free. No ranks. No performance.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-ctas">
          <a href="/compass" class="btn-ghost">Read The Compass</a>
          <a href="/join" class="btn-amber">Join a Chapter</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <span class="hero-cue" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================= WHAT THIS IS ========================= -->
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="lede-grid reveal">
        <aside class="lede-aside">
          <p class="kicker">What this is</p>
          <p class="lede-note">A book club for men. Weekly calls. Daily check-ins.</p>
        </aside>
        <div class="lede">
          <p class="lede-lead">
            At first, Crown and Compass is a small group of Christian men who read a book
            together and talk honestly about their lives. <em>No fees, no ranks, no performance.</em>
          </p>
          <p>
            A man shows up on a Saturday morning, hears other men speak plainly about what's
            hard and what they're grateful for, and realizes other men carry the same weight.
            That is the first thing it gives him.
          </p>
          <p>
            What it becomes over time is harder to name and more important. It becomes the
            community that makes the Walk possible. A man doesn't grow in isolation. He grows
            when other men are watching, asking, and walking alongside.
          </p>
          <p>
            This is not a guarantee of outcomes. It is a guarantee of accompaniment.
            We go together. That's the promise.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================= WHO IT'S FOR ========================= -->
  <section class="section-pad band-raise">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <p class="kicker kicker-rule">Who it's for</p>
        <h2>Three kinds of men find their way here.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="cards-grid-3">
        <AvatarCard
          number="01"
          headline="Built something, still feels it's not enough."
          description="A job, maybe a family, maybe a faith he grew up with but hasn't touched in years. Competent. Responsible. And a low-grade sense that something is missing. Most of his friendships are transactional."
        />
        <AvatarCard
          number="02"
          headline="In over his head, and unsure who to call."
          description="His marriage is strained, or his business is struggling, or his health is a mess he keeps meaning to address. He's tired of performing okay. He wants someone to ask the real question and mean it."
        />
        <AvatarCard
          number="03"
          headline="Doing well, and knows he can't sustain it alone."
          description="He's read the books, he goes to church, he's done some therapy. He knows the territory. What he needs is men doing the same work. Iron sharpens iron. He's looking for the iron."
        />
      </div>
      <p class="thread reveal">
        What these three men share: they want to be known, they want to grow, and they don't
        know where to find that among men.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================= HOW IT WORKS ========================= -->
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <p class="kicker kicker-rule">How it works</p>
        <h2>Four things, all connected.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="how-grid">
        <div class="how-cell reveal">
          <svg class="how-ic" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="3"/><circle cx="17" cy="7" r="3"/><path d="M1 21c0-4 3.6-7 8-7"/><path d="M23 21c0-4-3.6-7-8-7"/><path d="M7 21c0-3 2.2-5.5 5-5.5s5 2.5 5 5.5"/></svg>
          <h3>Chapters</h3>
          <p>Four to eight brothers who read the current book together and meet to discuss it. Weekly, or as the group can sustain. The core unit of Crown and Compass.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="how-cell reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <svg class="how-ic" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polygon points="16.24 7.76 14.12 14.12 7.76 16.24 9.88 9.88 16.24 7.76"/></svg>
          <h3>Guides</h3>
          <p>The Guide is not the teacher or the expert. He's the man who prepared, who holds the room, who keeps the conversation honest. Any brother can Guide. The role rotates.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="how-cell reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <svg class="how-ic" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/><circle cx="12" cy="16" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg>
          <h3>The Round</h3>
          <p>Closes every meeting. Three moves: the check-in (<em>where are you, really?</em>), The Ask, and The Close. The Round is where the real work happens.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="how-cell reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <svg class="how-ic" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/><path d="M12 2v4M12 18v4M2 12h4M18 12h4"/></svg>
          <h3>The Compass</h3>
          <p>The long-arc curriculum: four pillars, Body, Being, Balance, Business. A map, not a syllabus. The direction for the Walk.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ======================= THE COMPASS ========================== -->
  <section class="section-pad band-raise firelight">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <p class="kicker kicker-rule">The Compass</p>
        <h2>Four pillars. One long walk.</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">
          Not a self-help program. A map. A man picks it up knowing roughly where he stands,
          and uses it to walk.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-grid">
        <PillarCard name="Body" hook="Tend what you have been given. Not for aesthetics, for presence." href="/compass#body" />
        <PillarCard name="Being" hook="The inner life shapes everything downstream. Guard your heart." href="/compass#being" />
        <PillarCard name="Balance" hook="Who gets the actual you? The real one. The one who is present." href="/compass#balance" />
        <PillarCard name="Business" hook="Does your work serve your life, or have you become fuel for it?" href="/compass#business" />
      </div>
      <div class="compass-cta">
        <a href="/compass" class="btn-ghost">Read The Full Compass</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== A WORD FROM BRIAN ====================== -->
  <section class="section-pad firelight">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="quote-wrap reveal">
        <div class="quote-mark" aria-hidden="true">&ldquo;</div>
        <blockquote class="brian-quote">
          <p>I started Crown and Compass because I needed it. Not because I had answers, but because I was tired of carrying things alone.</p>
          <p>There's something that happens when a man says the true thing in a room of men who are glad he's there. I've seen it. It changes a man slowly, over time. The Walk is long. But something moves.</p>
          <p>What we're building is simple: a place where men can be honest with each other and with God, around a book, every week, for as long as it takes. That's it. That's enough.</p>
          <cite>Brian, Founder</cite>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========================= JOIN CTA =========================== -->
  <section class="section-pad band-raise close-cta firelight">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="close-inner reveal">
        <h2>Crown and Compass is free.<br />It has always been free.</h2>
        <p>
          Free because the Gospel is free. Free because the best communities have never charged
          for belonging. If you want to walk, reach out.
        </p>
        <a href="/join" class="btn-amber">Get Connected</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ---------- Hero ---------- */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 86vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(120% 90% at 50% -10%, rgba(201, 133, 58, 0.20), transparent 55%),
      radial-gradient(80% 60% at 50% 120%, rgba(201, 133, 58, 0.10), transparent 60%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0b10 0%, var(--bg-base) 60%, #0a0b10 100%);
  }
  .hero-rose {
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 0;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    width: min(74vw, 600px);
    height: min(74vw, 600px);
    transform: translate(-50%, -52%);
    color: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.06;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 6rem 0;
  }
  .hero-headline {
    font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
    line-height: 1.03;
    margin: 1.25rem 0 0;
  }
  .hero-subtext {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.2vw, 1.25rem);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 1.375rem auto 0;
    max-width: 34rem;
  }
  .hero-ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .hero-cue {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 1.75rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 1px;
    height: 46px;
    background: linear-gradient(var(--accent), transparent);
    opacity: 0.6;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* ---------- Section heads ---------- */
  .section-head { max-width: 40rem; margin-bottom: 2.75rem; }
  .section-head .kicker { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .section-sub {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 1rem 0 0;
  }

  /* ---------- What this is ---------- */
  .lede-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
  @media (min-width: 860px) {
    .lede-grid { grid-template-columns: 13rem 1fr; gap: 3.5rem; }
    .lede-aside { position: sticky; top: 6rem; align-self: start; }
  }
  .lede-aside .kicker { margin-bottom: 0.875rem; }
  .lede-note {
    font-family: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .lede { max-width: 40rem; }
  .lede p { color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0 0 1.25rem; }
  .lede-lead {
    font-family: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.3125rem, 2.6vw, 1.625rem);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text-primary) !important;
    margin-bottom: 1.625rem !important;
  }
  .lede-lead em { color: var(--accent); font-style: normal; }

  /* ---------- Who it's for ---------- */
  .cards-grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.125rem; }
  @media (min-width: 720px) { .cards-grid-3 { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); } }
  .thread {
    margin: 2.25rem 0 0;
    max-width: 46rem;
    font-family: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ---------- How it works ---------- */
  .how-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1px; background: var(--border-soft); border: 1px solid var(--border-soft); border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden; }
  @media (min-width: 620px) { .how-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  .how-cell { background: var(--bg-base); padding: 1.875rem 1.75rem; }
  .how-ic { width: 26px; height: 26px; color: var(--accent); display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .how-cell h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; }
  .how-cell p { font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.65; margin: 0; }
  .how-cell p em { color: var(--text-primary); font-style: italic; }

  /* ---------- Compass ---------- */
  .pillar-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
  @media (min-width: 560px) { .pillar-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  @media (min-width: 920px) { .pillar-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); } }
  .compass-cta { margin-top: 2rem; }

  /* ---------- Brian quote ---------- */
  .quote-wrap { max-width: 46rem; margin: 0 auto; }
  .quote-mark { font-family: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif; font-size: 5rem; line-height: 0.6; color: var(--accent); opacity: 0.5; height: 2rem; }
  .brian-quote { margin: 0; }
  .brian-quote p {
    font-family: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.6vw, 1.625rem);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
  }
  .brian-quote cite {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  /* ---------- Close CTA ---------- */
  .close-cta { text-align: center; }
  .close-inner { max-width: 40rem; margin: 0 auto; }
  .close-inner p {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 34rem;
    margin: 1.25rem auto 1.875rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
</style>
